  removed extra postinst

  09 Jul 2007; Steve Arnold <nerdboy@gentoo.org> geomview-1.9.2.ebuild:
  updated desktop entry and added calls to desktop_database_update

*geomview-1.9.2 (06 Jul 2007)

  06 Jul 2007; Steve Arnold <nerdboy@gentoo.org> +files/geomview.png,
